high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up the salt shaker from the counter
Move to the wooden shelf in the opposite side of the kitchen
Put the salt shaker on to the middle shelf
Move to the the cabinet to the right of the sink
Open the cabinet and pick up the salt shaker from inside and close the door
Move to the wooden shelf again in the opposite side of the kitchen
Place the salt shaker next to the first one on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the salt shakers from the counter and cabinet onto the wooden self.

high_descs: Turn right, walk past the stool across the room to the counter
Pick up the salt shaker on the counter next to the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the stove. Turn left and walk to the shelves across the room.
Set the salt shaker down on the middle shelf between the plate and the sponge
Turn around and walk back over to the counter behind you and follow it back to the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and open the cabinet under the drawer and take the salt shaker out of the cabinet.
Turn left and walk to the stove and then turn left and walk to the shelves.
Set the salt shaker down on the second shelf in front of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers next to each other on a shelf in the corner of the room.

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the opposite side of the room.
Pick up the salt shaker to the left of the microwave.
Turn left, head towards the stove, turn left head towards the wooden shelf.
Place the salt shaker in between the sponge and plate on the shelf.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Open the cabinet beneath the sink and take out the salt shaker from it.
Turn left, head towards the stove, turn left head towards the wooden shelf.
Place the salt shaker to the right of the shaker on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the two salt shakers on the wooden shelf.
